      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-cream/30">
        Weather data by <a href="https://open-meteo.com/" class="underline hover:text-honey transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open-Meteo</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp; Dashboard auto-refreshes weather on each visit
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-cream/20 mt-2">
        <!-- Replace this with owner photo and credit -->
